This Sleeping Beauty Turquoise Silver Squash Blossom Necklace Set is a sensational piece of quality hand made jewelry. This squash blossom necklace has a strong and fashionable look with hand cut oval cabochons of genuine Sleeping Beauty Turquoise. Each cab of this gorgeous creme of the crop number one grade Turquoise has been placed on an elegant oval setting of shimmering Sterling Silver. The hand stamped designs give this Necklace an elegant and graceful look. Sterling Silver bench beads give this squash blossom an extra high shine. This spectacular necklace is 28" long. The naja is 3" wide and 3" long. So, it hangs like a 33" long necklace. The matching Turquoise Earrings Bracelet and the Ring will be set to fit almost any size.
